            "query": "AppDependencies\n| where Name == \"agent.execute\"\n| summarize total = count(), failed = countif(Success == false) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)\n| extend ErrorPct = iff(total == 0, 0.0, round(100.0 * failed / total, 2))\n| project TimeGenerated, ErrorPct\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
